com.rscja.team.mtk.deviceapi

Class RFIDWithISO15693_mtk

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.rscja.team.mtk.deviceapi.RFIDBase_mtk
      • com.rscja.team.mtk.deviceapi.RFIDWithISO15693_mtk
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IRFIDBase, IRFIDWithISO15693

    public class RFIDWithISO15693_mtk
extends RFIDBase_mtk
implements IRFIDWithISO15693
    RFID模块ISO15693协议操作类,
    RFID module ISO15639 protocol operation type

    注意：
    Attention:
    1、使用前请确认您的机器已安装此模块。
    1. Make sure this module is installed before using your device.
    2、要正常使用模块需要在\libs\armeabi\目录放置libDeviceAPI.so文件
    2. Put libDeviceAPI.so file in directory \libs\armeabi\ then module can be used normally.
    3、在操作设备前需要调用 RFIDBase_mtk.init() 打开设备，使用完后调用 RFIDBase_mtk.free() 关闭设备
    3. Call RFIDBase_mtk.init() to switch on device before using device, call RFIDBase_mtk.free() to switch off the device after using.

    Author:
    liuruifeng
